{
  "title": "Article title (concise, SEO-friendly, no clickbait)",
  "keyword": "primary target keyword phrase",
  "outline": ["Section 1 heading", "Section 2 heading", ...],
  "angle": "The specific angle or hook for this article",
  "audience": "Target reader description",
  "key_points": ["Key point 1", "Key point 2", ...]
}

Return ONLY the JSON object, no markdown fences or other text.
